@page "/registry"

<div class="registry-page">
    <h1 class="registry-title">Registry</h1>
    <p class="registry-subtitle">Your presence is the real magic here.<br />But if you're feeling extra generous, we've curated some delightfully random treasures below.</p>

    <div class="registry-card">
        <div class="registry-logo-wrap">
            <img src="images/amazon.jpg" alt="Amazon" class="registry-logo" />
        </div>
        <p class="registry-description">
            We've conspired to assemble a wonderfully eclectic collection of curiosities and useful oddities on Amazon. From practical necessities to frivolous trinkets — there's something for every budget and every level of whimsy.
        </p>
        <a class="registry-btn" href="https://www.amazon.com/wedding/guest-view/3ARG58F8LFN8J" target="_blank">
            View Our Amazon Registry
        </a>
    </div>

    <p class="registry-note">
        Can't find something that speaks to your soul? A handwritten note full of mischief and well-wishes works just as well.
    </p>
</div>